getPrices((address[],address,address)[]).details: this method will return estimations for swap for one base token it can not be view, but to get estimation you have to call it in a static way Tokens that do not have `.decimals()` are not supported

params._data: array of PriceData, each PriceData can accept multiple pools per one price, price is fetched from pool, that has biggest liquidity (quote.balanceOf(pool)) TODO balanceOf might be not liquidity and by sending token to pool we can in theory affect this fetcher
